{"tid":165002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特首選舉】3.26投票日 500警力嚴陣以待 !!","createTime":"2017-03-21T05:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T06:50:16.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"085302acab260e9660aaff74daaa05c8dd43c810","tid":165002,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"今屆行政長官選舉結果將於<span style=\"color: green;\">本月26日</span>揭盅，近1,200名選委將到灣仔會展中心投票。民陣表明，當日會遊行至會展，但不會事先申請，僅會通知。 不過，有消息指，警方暫時據情報及風險評估，認為爆發大型示威衝突的機會不大，故暫只派港島總區應變大隊及其他相關部隊，共約500名人員負責會展外一帶的保安工作。而胡椒球發射器等防暴裝備，都會按屆時情況變化而備用。 <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/469499/xlarge/4726473646dc19ee6f27a960d8efdb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F469499%2Fxlarge%2F4726473646dc19ee6f27a960d8efdb2e.jpg&h=f2f206bb&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">3.26特首選舉投票日，警方將在灣仔會展一帶加強保安。（資料圖片）</span> 特首選舉日臨近，3名候選人的選舉工程如火如荼外，警方亦就當日保安措施密鑼緊鼓。選舉投票及點票將於灣仔會展舉行，據了解，警方當日在會場一帶的保安工作，將參考2012年行政長官選舉投票日，場內保安包括入場安檢等，會由會展的保安員負責，場外才是警隊主導。 <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/469610/xlarge/16d53e405562cdc21abfabf765c8f894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F469610%2Fxlarge%2F16d53e405562cdc21abfabf765c8f894.jpg&h=6ce63988&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">去年5月全國人大委員長張德江訪港期間，警方在灣仔北大規模部署保安區。（資料圖片） </span> <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/329833/xlarge/ab46a7132dcfb56d3d5f0a840b84232d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F329833%2Fxlarge%2Fab46a7132dcfb56d3d5f0a840b84232d.jpg&h=8e04a4a0&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">過去2年多，香港經歷多次大型示威，警隊曾向衝擊者使用不同程度武力。不論是雨傘運動中發射催淚彈或旺角衝突中交通警向天開槍，警隊均指使用的武力恰當，亦拒絕公開武力指引。（資料圖片）</span> <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/141823/xlarge/4151f58d1f211d99aa411b12af65f801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F141823%2Fxlarge%2F4151f58d1f211d99aa411b12af65f801.jpg&h=3ea170e4&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">若出現衝突場面，警方將視情況使用不同程度的武力控制場面。（資料圖片）</span> <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/169529/xlarge/6e3b719071df561e228660f85ea28d56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F169529%2Fxlarge%2F6e3b719071df561e228660f85ea28d56.jpg&h=617e5f58&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">警方過去多次用上縮警棍及盾牌。（資料圖片）</span> <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/32387/xlarge/25c2dea3c1d7d6748c4ebd22609b0267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F32387%2Fxlarge%2F25c2dea3c1d7d6748c4ebd22609b0267.jpg&h=ddde320a&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">若經警告未果，警方或使用胡椒噴霧以即時遏止衝擊。（資料圖片）</span> <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/272120/xlarge/5dcb0a79531227d6b8aab4e3014a3fd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F272120%2Fxlarge%2F5dcb0a79531227d6b8aab4e3014a3fd6.jpg&h=d7115c66&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">去年11月反釋法遊行後，警方在西區警署外以胡板噴霧驅趕示威者。（資料圖片／李澤彤攝）</span> <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/272238/xlarge/e53276a99b8e501024941a7684fa4c9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F272238%2Fxlarge%2Fe53276a99b8e501024941a7684fa4c9e.jpg&h=acc2f66e&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">在處理反釋法遊行示威，速龍小隊配備「大口槍」法德魯槍等及「胡椒球」。（互聯網圖片）</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">民陣不申請不反對通知書</span> 不過，有別於往屆選舉的場外示威，今年民間人權陣線不會事先申請。據民陣就下周一記者會的採訪通知，表明將在投票日，由灣仔家計會遊行至會展，惟不會預先向警方申請「不反對通知書」，僅會「通知」，而具體遊行路線未定，主要是警方未公開當日佈防。 警方消息則指，由於暫未有團體向警方申請示威，警方未在會展外劃出確實示威區，若稍後有團體「入紙」，警方傾向參考上屆做法。據上屆選舉日，示威團體主要在港灣道消防局外請願。 <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/469651/xlarge/47c303d674afb0f78f42711297f2ba40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F469651%2Fxlarge%2F47c303d674afb0f78f42711297f2ba40.jpg&h=f003de68&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">去年張德江訪港時民陣亦有發起集會。（資料圖片）</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">港島應變大隊全出 其餘4陸上總區候命</span> 據了解，警方分析過投票日的風險及情報，預期當日會發生大型衝突機會不大，故暫只由港島總區應變大隊負責場外保安，隊員來自機動部隊、衝鋒隊、快速應變隊、刑事偵緝隊等，連同協助交通封路的交通部、軍裝巡警等，共出動約500人。不過為預留足夠警力應付突發大型示威及衝突，警隊其餘4個陸上總區的應變大隊、「速龍小隊」亦會候命。 此外，警方現時有胡椒球發射器、催淚彈等防暴裝備，消息指應變大隊均配有相關裝備，屆時按情況，如有需要，都會動用。 <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/287015/xlarge/873822dd18d34b8758b6bf1bdfcc88a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F287015%2Fxlarge%2F873822dd18d34b8758b6bf1bdfcc88a4.jpg&h=6498d5b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">去年11月的反釋法遊行，警方速龍小隊配備「胡椒球發射器」。(資料圖片)</span> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/78092/-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-3-26%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E6%97%A5-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-500%E8%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E5%9A%B4%E9%99%A3%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F78092%2F-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-3-26%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B-500%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2599%25A3%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25BE%2585&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=daa4287f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/78092/-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-3-26%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E6%97%A5-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-500%E8%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E5%9A%B4%E9%99%A3%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%85</a>"},{"pid":"b07c7e1bc6fe0cb1d7e744866b9d4b5df9e40567","tid":165002,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:04:58.000Z","msg":"今年應該無乜人去示威"},{"pid":"d71b69e46dc61a7045e2a15f21a945ab65760a31","tid":165002,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"示威係可以，但我搞唔清佢哋嘅取向係乜？<br />\n如果林鄭贏，係咪會升級？如果薯片、胡官贏，係咪就散水？<br />\n定係純粹向當選人表達完訴求就算？"},{"pid":"8137e1ce3f865f3822adc88812230d750871bbda","tid":165002,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"熱普賤三個共匪特務黨死釘本土獨立派<br />\n<br />\n泛民就和理非唱歌<br />\n<br />\n黑警都唔知驚乜?"},{"pid":"b15a93fca4d6484da2cc65aa775d89e465186de1","tid":165002,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4x561pnm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4x561pnm&h=44b765b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bf56347ad6d4dd5114e931743d68e2eb6c2b474","tid":165002,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:50:16.000Z","msg":"我估冇人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}